OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a little drizzle
OL,6,Facross the north at first. Otherwise
OL,7,Fit will be dry and rather cloudy but
OL,8,Fsome sunny spells developing this
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness in places. Then
OL,13,Fthe rest of the night will be mainly
OL,14,Fdry but the odd shower possible in the
OL,15,Fnorth later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FChance of a light shower in
OL,18,Fthe north at first otherwise dry with
OL,19,Fsome sunshine by afternoon. Patchy
OL,20,Flight rain in the evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
