OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Saturday with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading southeast at times. A few
OL,8,Fearly showers on Sunday otherwise dry.
OL,9,FChance of rain on Monday.
